  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Administrative roles:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist HR with staff leave process, expenses and reimbursement.</li>\n  <li>Preparation of basic quotations, contracts and tender submissions.</li>\n  <li>Assist team on correspondence and delivery schedules.</li>\n  <li>Sourcing, ordering and delivering of project related materials.</li>\n  <li>Record minutes of meetings and prepare emails, faxes, correspondence, memos, etc.</li>\n  <li>Manage and maintain office stationeries and pantry supplies</li>\n  <li>To assist and work together with ISO team</li>\n  <li>To manage and maintain good housekeeping of the entire office together with Admin Manager</li>\n  <li>To handle and managed oversea courier services</li>\n  <li>To handle phone queries and attend to guests</li>\n  <li>Provide administrative and clerical support to HR/Admin manager</li>\n  <li>To maintain and manage office equipment</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc admin duties assigned by Directors or HODs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PA roles:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Co-ordinate and manage MD and EDs’ daily paperwork, emails and claims.</li>\n  <li>Organize seminars and travel arrangement, hotels and travel expenses report for MD and ED.</li>\n  <li>Prepare presentation materials for MD and ED including tender documents with respective team members.</li>\n  <li>Manage phone and emails correspondence for MD and ED</li>\n  <li>Manage and arrange appointments with internal and external parties</li>\n  <li>Manage and spearhead company’s events and activities with team / committee from planning to execution and completion.</li>\n  <li>Managing and reviewing filing system and archives.</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc duties assigned by MD and ED.</li>\n</ul>",
